Is my bank data safe? Do I need to link my bank credentials?
Your data is completely safe because Fin OS never asks for your bank login credentials. We do not use third-party aggregators to scrape your accounts. You can track your wealth via safe CSV statement imports or manual entry, ensuring your bank credentials remain 100% private.

How does the AI DNA Analysis work?
Our Financial Brain analyzes your spending velocity, calculates your emergency runway (Burn Rate), and detects "Lifestyle Inflation." All of this mathematical processing happens locally on your phone's processor.

What is the F.I.R.E. Number in the Decision Tab?
F.I.R.E. stands for Financial Independence, Retire Early. The app uses the globally recognized "4% Rule," which calculates that you need approximately 25 times your annual expenses invested in order to retire safely without running out of money. The simulator tracks your live progress toward this exact goal.

How does the Debt Crusher work?
The Debt Crusher organizes your liabilities using the Avalanche Method. It analyzes all your credit cards and loans, sorts them by the highest interest rate, and tells you exactly which one to pay off first to save the most money on interest.

Can I export my data for my accountant?
Yes! Go to the Hub / More Tab and tap Export PDF. Fin OS will instantly generate a beautifully formatted, professional PDF statement of your Net Worth and recent transactions that you can share via WhatsApp, Email, or save to your files.

Will I lose my data if I change phones?
If you have created an account and enabled Cloud Sync, your encrypted database will securely move to your new device when you log in.
